
force add-captioning-change-listener
  mount build, field captioning-manager
  mount listener, field captioning-manager-captioning-change-listener

  cause call-method
    drive object, share build
    drive method, |addCaptioningChangeListener|
    drive factor, share listener
    raise build, field unit

